title: Bringing Out The Best In People | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Bringing Out The Best In People | Joel Osteen
description:
You have something to offer the people in your life that no one else can give. When you take time to build up and encourage others, you're empowering them to become all that God created them to be. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
